!!!
%html
  %head
    %title BAMRU Location Tracker
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0", :name => "viewport"}/
    / Bootstrap
    %link{:href => "//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
      %link{:href => "//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/3.2.1/css/font-awesome.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}/
      %link{:href => "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Abel|Open+Sans:400,600", :rel => "stylesheet"}/
      :css
        /* http://css-tricks.com/perfect-full-page-background-image/ */
        html {
        	background: url("http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3678/9071700493_2044321565_h.jpg") no-repeat center center fixed; 
        	-webkit-background-size: cover;
        	-moz-background-size: cover;
        	-o-background-size: cover;
        	background-size: cover;
        }

        body {
        	padding-top: 20px;
        	font-size: 16px;
        	font-family: "Open Sans",serif;
        	background: transparent;
        }

        h1 {
        	font-family: "Abel", Arial, sans-serif;
        	font-weight: 400;
        	font-size: 40px;
        }

        /* Override B3 .panel adding a subtly transparent background */
        .panel {
        	background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        .margin-base-vertical {
        	margin: 40px 0;
        }

	  %body
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.panel.panel-default
          %h1.margin-base-vertical Have you ever seen the rain?
          %p
            Someone told me long ago there's a calm before the storm. I know, It's been comin for some time.
          %p
            When it's over, so they say, it'll rain a sunny day. I know,	Shinin down like water.
          %p
            I want to know, have you ever seen the rain?
          %form.margin-base-vertical
            %p.input-group
              %span.input-group-addon
                %span.icon-envelope
              %input.form-control.input-lg{:name => "email", :placeholder => "jonsnow@knowsnothi.ng", :type => "text"}/
            %p.help-block.text-center
              %small We won't send you spam. Unsubscribe at any time.
            %p.text-center
              %button.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{:type => "submit"} Keep me posted
          .margin-base-vertical
            %small.text-muted
              %a{:href => "http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3678/9071700493_2044321565_h.jpg"}> Background picture by Nick Freeman @flickr
              \. Used under
              = succeed "." do
                %a{:href => "http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/deed.en"} Creative Commons - Attribution
        / //main content
      / //row
    / //container